error.message: Parameter $entity_manager of method Drupal\facebook_instant_articles\Plugin\views\row\FiaFields::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityManagerInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to facebook_instant_articles.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
